OOC: Nice to see you again Teltoli!

:::Starscream/Vulois:::

Starscream: Alright!  This'll be FUN!
::he follows Dollen out the exit::
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
::Vulois was about to give up on his friends when he hears a familiar voice::
Vulois: Battera and Cybershark!  Great to see you two again.
::He looks at Cybershark::
Vulois: It looks like you've got a new form.  Now, the reason i called you 
here is because i have regained all of my old memories back.  I remember 
everything that happened before the Alliance reprogrammed me.  I would like 
to start my old agenda up again.  I'm returning to my mountain lair to start 
peace talks one more.  I have a new plan.  We all go to each faction 
together.  the splitting up got us into trouble last time.  Soundwave was 
killed.  I will not let what happened to him happen to you two.  So what do 
you say?  Will you join me?

--part1_e4.e0ccedf.27663691_boundary
